Requires:         R-MASS 
Requires:         R-parallel 
Requires:         R-CRAN-SCEPtER 

%description
SCEPtER pipeline for estimating the stellar age for double-lined detached
binary systems. The observational constraints adopted in the recovery are
the effective temperature, the metallicity [Fe/H], the mass, and the
radius of the two stars. The results are obtained adopting a maximum
likelihood technique over a grid of pre-computed stellar models.

